Normal procedure in longwave:

1. Create hybrid file of well-mixed gases for median atmosphere,
e.g. using CKDMIP's "ckdmip_tool --merge-only"

2. Use src/ecckd/reorder_spectrum_lw via test/reorder_spectrum_lw.sh
to create reordered spectra for the median profile of H2O, O3 and the
hybrid gas

3. Use src/ecckd/find_g_points_lw via

   test/find_g_points_lw.sh MODEL_CODE=test